--- In nbwrpg@y..., "LurkerAbyss" <1641coburn@h...> wrote:
> ::Hakibuscon::
> 
>     Hakibuscon approached the Decepticon base with caution, 
transforming to robot mode.  He activated his stealth mode, which 
made him invisible to the defenses.  He sent a message through to all 
Decepticons in the Dark Avian.
> 
>     "Fellow Decepticons!  Do you hear me?  It's me, Wingspan!  I'm 
alive!  I've got a new body, but I'm still a Decepticon, always and 
forever!" Hakibuscon said, faking his identity.  He learned that a 
bounty hunter should never reveal his true identity.
